name: Fivethirtysomething
body:
The two party system has failed us and we have a crisis of leadership at all levels of government in this country. It's on our generation to find the solutions for an economy that's rapidly changing
 Join us in nominating friends, family and loved ones to run for office at all levels of government. We need a new generation of leadership from across the political spectrum made up of Independents, Republicans, Democrats, Conservatives, Liberals and Moderates.
 We're still figuring this out, sign up and help find a better solution.
